a","tid":389274,"uid":72445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T11:42:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>十年人事幾翻身 突然跌親咪起返身 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n十年人事幾番新 十年過得幾艱辛</blockquote><br />\n皇后碼頭要拆 灣仔果條印刷 街又要拆<br />\n會變成乜野風格<br />\n維多利亞海港 每年都transform 好似變型金剛 變成維多利亞河<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97b0f6fafd4a153c9079bc79bfabd66bebfc6930","tid":389274,"uid":140470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T11:44:40.000Z","msg":"細個我嘅伴侶 係一堆玩具<br />\n到大個我嘅伴侶 係一堆負累"},{"pid":"74343cd950cda5163242766fbe62ea51f198b609","tid":389274,"uid":23902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T11:45:49.000Z","msg":"原來做功課好簡單 做人好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b29e1b3bae7180f24219439ba9c9fcbb9fe0e400","tid":389274,"uid":1249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T11:47:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個聽佢地啲歌覺得佢啲歌好無厘頭，但而家聽落原來每句歌詞都好有意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似喺YouTube留言見過依個comment<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb1a499aa93528ad166f232ae4208249b979da7c","tid":389274,"uid":80162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T11:47:33.000Z","msg":"我嘅女人唔使聽曬我話 OK OK<br />\n要有品 唔一定要留係屋企捉棋<br />\n得閑煮翻幾味 就算有怪味<br />\n只要食唔死我都唔會怪你<br />\n你唔使身材苗條到似瑤瑤<br />\n我只係需要攬住你條腰<br />\n我講笑你識笑 我rap你聽<br />\n唔識跳唔緊要 只要你跟住搖<br />\n唔會介意你有時好似仔<br />\n因為我只係想你hold me tight<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"346d95133aef0a94607959cde7622b3293dd0dd9","tid":389274,"uid":20938,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T11:48:41.000Z","msg":"唔想大係長大既證據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"856c398ac191195429a9d3754669338258e1de54","tid":389274,"uid":12833,"like"